        <TD bgcolor='dimgray' valign='top' nowrap><b><font color='white' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='2'>Kaallan</font></b></td>
        <TD bgcolor='dimgray' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='2'>My two copper.  I am helping PL a ranger friend who is 23rd level.  I am a 49th level necro.  I take him to the 8 skellie spawn in the Rathe Mountains (where the giant skellies, skeletal monks, etc. spawn).  They are all red and yellow to him.  There is some trash but the spawn is so quick it doesnt matter.  </P><P>I bring up 49th level pet and pull the skellie with first level dark spell.  I then sic the pet on it and root.  It takes a little practice but once the mob is at about 20% back the pet off (the root should still be holding).  Cast screaming terror on it and tell your friend to go.  The spawn rate is insane and you can single pull to your hearts content.  A warrior should be able to level in an hour or so here (a little slower as he gets up).  This is good leveling until about 28 or 29.</P><P>Kaallan L'EssHue<BR>49th Dark Elf Necro<BR>Karana</P><P>With the pricking of a thumb, something wicked this way comes</font></td>
